STATE
v.
BONNELL 2017-1360 Supreme Court of Ohio. December 12, 2018

RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISION

On appellant's motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.

O'CONNOR, C.J., and FRENCH and DEGENARO, JJ., dissent and would grant the motion in part and would clarify the analysis in paragraph 26 of the court's opinion.
